ADHDSx_18: Interrupt or intrude on others (butt into conversations or activities without permission or take over what others are doing).
ADHDSx_19: Prone to daydreaming when I should be concentrating on something or working.
ADHDSx_20: Have trouble staying alert or awake in boring situations.
ADHDSx_25: Underactive or have less energy than others.
ADHDSx_27: I don’t seem to process information as quickly or as accurately as others.
